title: Ulysses 1781 Cyclops Part 1 (2015) (Sosich) cbr
description:
1781,YORKTOWN, THE AMERICAN WAR OF INDEPENDENCE HAS JUST ENDED. VICTORIOUS,
CAPTAIN ULYSSES McHENDRICS IS READY TO RETURN HOME WITH HIS SON AND HIS MEN.
BUT THE RETURN IS HASTENED WHEN HE LEARNS THAT HIS TOWN, NEW ITHACA, IS
INVATDED BY THE ENGLISH.
ULYSSES AND HIS MEN WILL HAVE TO CROSS FANTASTIC AMERICA WHERE COMPASSES
DON'T FIND NORTH ANYMORE, WHERE MAPS LOST THEIR PATHS, A WORLD BETWEEN
REALITY AND MYSTERY...

enjoy
